{"tid":1065820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平凡台灣女孩】凌友詩被罰$12.7萬決上訴 台內政部：中國沒這機會","createTime":"2019-03-17T13:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T01:25:13.000Z","uid":51620,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0c075c53111df70e0e9bfeed805a28b0136dd7","tid":1065820,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190317/59378513?fbclid=IwAR3sScUgUkbGqfLr-1GmAO2Pj1tLwYank1gRw6TBFByXntHHwCiKBffNX4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59378513%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3sScUgUkbGqfLr-1GmAO2Pj1tLwYank1gRw6TBFByXntHHwCiKBffNX4s&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=62299a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59378513%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3sScUgUkbGqfLr-1GmAO2Pj1tLwYank1gRw6TBFByXntHHwCiKBffNX4s&h=4b9f81ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190317/59378513?fbclid=IwAR3sScUgUkbGqfLr-1GmAO2Pj1tLwYank1gRw6TBFByXntHHwCiKBffNX4s</a><br />\n<br />\n領有台灣護照的57歲的「平凡台灣女孩」、中國全國政協委員凌友詩，近日遭台灣內政部以違反《台灣地區與大陸地區人民關係條例》開罰50萬元新台幣（約12.7萬港元）。凌友詩接受港媒訪問反擊，將保留上訴的權利。對此，台灣內政部次長陳宗彥表示，上訴是中華民國國民依照憲法與民主法治下擁有的基本權益，凌女當然有權回到台灣提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n凌友詩擁有中華民國戶籍，又同時擔任中國第13屆全國政協委員職務，在3月11日的中國全國政協全體會議上發表演說，<span style=\"color: red;\">違反《兩岸條例》中「不得擔任中共黨政軍職務」規定</span>，因此內政部依法裁處最高額度的50萬元罰款。<br />\n<br />\n凌女表示將提出上訴，陳宗彥回覆，經查證後發現凌女目前仍保留台灣戶籍及國籍，適用兩岸條例規定，政府依法所作出的處分，人民仍有上訴的渠道，這就是台灣民主法治的價值，在中國大陸可沒有此機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友仲夠唔夠膽返去臺灣"},{"pid":"a4ed6b770c16de624ae9853d3dff829457dc1d13","tid":1065820,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"57步女孩"},{"pid":"bab1992a64126947084b207706ac245326c7740c","tid":1065820,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>57歲女孩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"50f26b6cc0ab666f89fbafe974c3f411bd6ff199","tid":1065820,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4ed6b770c16de624ae9853d3dff829457dc1d13","tid":1065820,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"57步女孩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更年期都過左仲叫自己做女孩"},{"pid":"482df0df1f16120b73e64598bc7451eb26c35e68","tid":1065820,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9425317c3714079487510282a93a048850c24c","tid":1065820,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"上次罰12萬, 今次取消埋台灣戶籍"},{"pid":"ace258e9290681faf21c1dcd3de0923f149c353e","tid":1065820,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"50萬新台幣對佢來講濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c611953737530b2205ce1765880f2db5399fdfd","tid":1065820,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"取消户藉啦"},{"pid":"2ffc52fd25fbd14af0a5990986de5ca247b5c8cf","tid":1065820,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"cut鳩佢福利啦，呢d仆街同班新殖民一樣一有病一定唔敢o係支那醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm